# Attachments Catalog

> **Purpose:** Committed catalog of Jira-task attachments (logs, screenshots, videos, DB snapshots, configs). The actual binary files live in `./attachments/` (gitignored). This catalog travels with the spec so reviewers on PR and future sessions know what evidence exists, with hashes for drift detection.
>
> **Lifecycle:** Created by `jira-intake` Phase 5g. Updated by `jira-intake-resync` when reporter adds/modifies attachments in Jira. Read by specs-management Step 0.

